\c 34
\s Kufa nokuvigwa kwaMozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mozisi wakabva pamapani okwaMoabhu, akakwira kugomo reNebho, pamusoro pePisiga, pakatarisana neJeriko. Jehovha akamuratidza nyika yose yeGiriyadhi, kusvikira Dhani;
\v 2 neNafutari yose, nenyika yaEfuremu naManase, nenyika yose yaJudha, kusvikira pagungwa rokumavirazuva;
\v 3 nenyika yezasi, neBani romupata weJeriko, guta remichindwe, kusvikira Zoari.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha akati kwaari, Ndiyo nyika yandakapikira Abhurahama, naIsaka, naJakove, ndichiti, Ndichaipa vana vako; ndikakuonesa iyo nameso ako, asi haungapindimo.
\p
\v 5 Ipapo Mozisi muranda waJehovha akafirapo panyika yaMoabhu, sezvakataurwa naJehovha.
\v 6 Akamuviga pamupata panyika yaMoabhu, pakatarisana neBheti-peori, asi hapana munhu unoziva rinda rake kusvikira nhasi.
\v 7 Zvino Mozisi wakange ana makore ane zana namakumi maviri pakufa kwake; meso ake akange achigere kuonera madzerere, nesimba rake rakange richigere kuderera.
\p
\v 8 Vana vaIsraeri vakachema Mozisi pamapani okwaMoabhu mazuva ana makumi matatu; naizvozvo mazuva avakachema pakuchema Mozisi akapera.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Joshua, mwanakomana waNuni, wakange azere nomweya wokuchenjera; nekuti Mozisi wakange aisa maoko ake pamusoro pake; vana vaIsraeri vakamuteerera, vakaita sezvakarairwa Mozisi naJehovha.
\p
\v 10 Hakuna kuzomukazve muporofita pakati paIsraeri wakafanana naMozisi, wakange achizikanwa naJehovha, zviso zvakatarisana;
\v 11 pazviratidzo zvose nezvishamiso, paakatumwa naJehovha kundozviita panyika yeEgipita, kuna Farao, nokuvaranda vake vose, nokunyika yake yose;
\v 12 napazvose zvakaitwa noruoko rwake rune simba, napakutyisa kukuru kose, kwakaitwa naMozisi valsiraeri vose vachizviona.
